protected_spaces_details.description: Outdoor sports facilities incl school playing fields

description: Submission of Reserved Matters (Phase 2) pursuant to Condition 1 of Outline planning permission dated 24th June 2009 (Ref. 08/2782/O) for the erection of 595 residential units, including 170 extra care units, and 90.9 square metres of community floorspace (Use Class D1), associated car parking, cycle parking and servicing, a childrens' play area, and creation of public open space to be provided as part of the approved Kidbrooke Masterplan.
